data.description: Outstanding, mountain home with amazing long range views! This home is in immaculate condition. It's located on a large property (3 lots) in the high Tusquittee mountains near Hayesville, NC. Impressive, wood burning, stone fireplace is the centerpiece of the large living room. Cathedral, wood paneled ceiling. Plenty of glass for natural light. Beautiful hardwood floors. Open kitchen and dining room. Main floor master bedroom and bath. Two (2) upper floor bedrooms and bath. The spacious rear deck affords terrific, year-round, southern views of the distant valley and mountains. And a full basement, ready for storage or easy completion, to significantly increase your inside living space. You'll find it impossible to find a better mountain property, with such tremendous long range views, in this price range.
